        "Describe this image in detail.  and write an image text prompt based on this image. 2 tasks\n\n### Image Description:\nThe image features a young woman standing outdoors in front of a modern building with large glass windows. She has her hair styled in a high bun and is looking directly at the camera with a neutral expression. She is wearing a white cropped tank top and high-waisted denim shorts with frayed edges. Over her top, she has a purple varsity jacket with black and white striped cuffs and collar. The jacket has a large letter \"B\" on the left chest and a circular emblem on the right sleeve. The background is slightly blurred, emphasizing the subject in the foreground.\n\n### Image Text Prompt:\nWrite a detailed description of the image, including the subject's appearance, hairstyle, and clothing. Mention the color and design of the varsity jacket and the overall style of the outfit. Describe the background and how it contributes to the composition of the image.\n\n### Task 1:\nDescribe the main elements in the image, focusing on the subject and her attire.\n\n### Task 2:\nWrite a creative caption for the image, highlighting the stylish and youthful vibe of the outfit and the urban setting."
